        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Wishing to borrow a compass. Colonization.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Bravo</placeName> <date when="1826-01-14">January 14th 1826</date></p>
<p><persName>Col Austin</persName></p>

<p>Dear Sir <persName>Mr. Cox</persName> one of the <persName>companyof the <placeName>upper colony</placeName></persName> 
wishes me to Doo Som surveying for him and <persName>others </persName>and I Have
no other chance of gitting a compass Except from you allso considerably for <persName>coln coals[Coln Coles]</persName>  if you can accommodate me
with one you will confur a favor on yours and please Send it By
<persName>Mr. Milacan</persName>   if you have none Be so good as to Try to pocure one <pb n="1257"/>
for me a short time as I can com pleat the work in 3 or 4 weaks at
farthest</p>

<p>your at ten tion to this will con fur a favor on yours &amp;c</p>

<p><persName>Bartlett Sims</persName>    [Rubric]</p>
<p>thar is 5 or Six <persName>familys </persName>up <placeName>in this part of the countray</placeName> wishin
to Settle in your <placeName>Colony</placeName> and ar making thar Selections up <placeName>near
the Road on thoas creeks that form the yea way [Yegua</placeName> ]</p>

<p><persName>Sims</persName></p>


        </div1>
